{notable.map((alumni)=>{ return (
{alumni.name}

Web Designer

Information

{alumni.branch}

Year

{alumni.year-4}-{alumni.year}
Projects

Recent

Sam Disuja

Most Viewed

Dinoter husainm
) })}
) } export default NotableAlumni
